---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | PT. Zaada Bana Engineering">
  <main class="text-center">
    <div
      class="hero relative bg-no-repeat bg-center text-white py-32 z-0"
      style="background-image: url('/online-colleges-leadership-degree-blog4-1900x900.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;"
    >
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/50 to-transparent"
      >
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 py-20">
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold leading-tight">About Us</h1>
        <p class="text-xl mt-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          PT. Zaada Bana Engineering is a company engaged in electrical construction engineering. We are committed to being the First Choice Partner in the electrical construction field.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="py-20 px-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-8">Our Story</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Since 2017, PT. Zaada Bana Engineering has continuously developed its business in the electrical field, covering planning, construction, and maintenance services. The experiences and lessons learned during our early growth have enabled the company to continuously grow and develop.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        In line with rapid development, a broad chain and network are needed in the scope of services, including consulting for planning systems, implementation, and after-sales services. With increasing trust and a desire to develop the business better, we continue to innovate in terms of services and products. PT. Zaada Bana Engineering is also committed to contributing to the field of new and renewable energy. Through this contribution, we hope to provide the community with a point of view on the importance of energy.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 px-8 bg-gray-100">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 text-left">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-4">Our Vision</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            BECOME FIRST CHOICE PARTNER AND SOLUTION IN ELECTRICAL PROFESSIONAL WORKING, TOGETHER BUILD OUR NATION.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-2">
            <li>Deliver best quality and fast excellent services to customer</li>
            <li>Always keep and put solution oriented mindset first to customer</li>
            <li>Develop and strengthening our talent to give and deliver best service to customer</li>
            <li>Improve and innovate through the product</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 px-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-8">Our Expertise</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
        With the support of professional experts and a complete workshop, PT. Zaada Bana Engineering is always committed to providing the best service to our partners.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg flex flex-col items-center">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 text-primary-dark mb-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" /></svg>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-2">Skilled Professionals</h3>
          <p class="text-md text-center">Our team comprises highly qualified and experienced engineers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg flex flex-col items-center">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 text-primary-dark mb-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.343 3.94c.07-.327.227-.605.412-.83.19-.233.39-.44.6-.636.21-.196.42-.38.63-.55.21-.17.42-.32.63-.45.21-.13.42-.24.63-.33.21-.09.42-.16.63-.21.21-.05.42-.08.63-.09.21-.01.42-.01.63-.01.21 0 .42 0 .63.01.21.01.42.04.63.09.21.05.42.16.63.21.21.13.42.24.63.33.21.17.42.38.63.55.21.196.41-.403.6-.636.185-.225.342-.503.412-.83m-1.45 1.45c-.07.327-.227.605-.412.83-.19.233-.39.44-.6-.636-.21-.196-.42-.38-.63-.55-.21-.17-.42-.32-.63-.45-.21-.13-.42-.24-.63-.33-.21-.09-.42-.16-.63-.21-.21-.05-.42-.08-.63-.09-.21-.01-.42-.01-.63-.01-.21 0-.42 0-.63.01-.21.01-.42.04-.63.09-.21.05-.42.16-.63.21-.21.13-.42.24-.63.33-.21.17-.42.38-.63.55-.21.196-.41-.403-.6-.636-.185-.225-.342-.503-.412-.83m-1.45 1.45c-.07.327-.227.605-.412.83-.19.233-.39.44-.6-.636-.21-.196-.42-.38-.63-.55-.21-.17-.42-.32-.63-.45-.21-.13-.42-.24-.63-.33-.21-.09-.42-.16-.63-.21-.21-.05-.42-.08-.63-.09-.21-.01-.42-.01-.63-.01-.21 0-.42 0-.63.01-.21.01-.42.04-.63.09-.21.05-.42.16-.63.21-.21.13-.42.24-.63.33-.21.17-.42.38-.63.55-.21.196-.41-.403-.6-.636-.185-.225-.342-.503-.412-.83" /></svg>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-2">Advanced Technology</h3>
          <p class="text-md text-center">Utilizing the latest tools and techniques for optimal results.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg flex flex-col items-center">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 text-primary-dark mb-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-2">Comprehensive Solutions</h3>
          <p class="text-md text-center">From planning to maintenance, we cover all aspects of electrical engineering.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>